column1:
Those scumbags are feeding off your pain,
and that of other decent human beings.

They drain the lives of those around them like
parasites, all for their own petty convenience.
So don't let them take advantage of you!
You need to come home with me!
After all this, you still won't see things my way!

I won't believe you... I can't! With the power
I have, I can finally change the bad people's
hearts!

If that bothers you, then come and get me!
But fair warning: I'll change your heart before
you even know it!

She disappeared! Was she some sorta
hologram?

We are, but what about you? That outfit of
yours...

Belongs in a museum, I know. But forget about
that—let's get you outta there.

Looks like it's electronically locked. Hold on,
I'll get it open in a jiffy!
I knew you'd come to our rescue!
Of course... I'm so glad you're all okay!
Hey, you can always count on me!
Totally! I am a phantom thief, after all.
We narrowly escaped a dark fate.

Yeah. I thought I'd be stuck in a Jail all over
again.

We heard you were arrested. You had us
worried sick...

Well, thanks to you, I got out. Gotta tip my hat
to your older sister, too.
Good going, Sis. I knew you could do it!

But damn, Gramps, I nearly dropped a brick
when you showed up.

Hey, I'm just as flabbergasted as you. And
what's with the chained-up knight thing?

That's the rebel in your heart awakened:
the power of your Persona.

Hey, fine by me. I don't understand a damn
thing, but if it can help me fight, I'll take it.
Sooo, you guys know what this means.
He needs an official code name!

I do? Oh, right—whenever you're in uniform,
you always call each other something different.
Then go ahead and call me "Wolf."

Those endless days of barking on command are
done. From now on, lone wolf or not, my fangs
will shred all evil!
Heh, I like the sound'a that!
Yeah, that totally puts it in perspective!

All right, then. Welcome to the Phantom
Thieves.

Not to change the subject, but I want to get back
to Akane.
Why the hell am I... so exhausted?

It's all part of the process of awakening your
Persona. Takes quite a toll on your psyche.

We should head back to the real world and
rest.
No! I'll be fine... Akane comes first.
We all know how you feel.

We can't fail this mission if we want to save
Akane-chan's life.

Let's come back when we're able to fight at our
best.
